This is my bash settings for sharing various systems.

make_link.rb
  - link generate for bash shell in linux and windows

.bashrc for bashrc
  - ls alias

.ctags for ctags
  - add javascript pattern
  - add xul to HTML format

.gitconfig for git
  - add some alias

.screenrc for screen daemon
  - status bar setting
  - session changing key binding
  - grow up scroll buffer

.vimrc, .vim for vim
  - various plugin and settings
